<i>adverb</i>: 하염없이 [하여멉씨], 우두커니 [우두커니], 오도카니 [오도카니], 멍히 [멍ː히], 멍하니 [멍ː하니], 멍청히 [멍청히], 멀뚱멀뚱 [멀뚱멀뚱], 멀거니 [멀거니], 망연히 [망연히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>하염없이 [하여멉씨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. absent-mindedly; blankly; vacantly</dd><br>
<dd>걱정에 싸여 아무 생각이 없이 멍하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Absent-mindedly without any thoughts, being worried about something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. endlessly; incessantly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 행동이나 감정 등이 그치지 않고 계속되는 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which a certain act or emotion continues without stopping.</dd><br>
<dt>우두커니 [우두커니]</dt><br>
<dd>blankly; vacantly</dd><br>
<dd>넋이 나간 듯이 한 자리에 가만히 서 있거나 앉아 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of standing or sitting in a place without movement as if one is absent-minded.</dd><br>
<dt>오도카니 [오도카니]</dt><br>
<dd>vacantly; blankly</dd><br>
<dd>한 자리에 가만히 멈추어 멍하게 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which one does not move absent-mindedly in one place.</dd><br>
<dt>멍히 [멍ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. blankly</dd><br>
<dd>정신이 나간 것처럼 반응이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without a response as if one lost one's mind.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in a puzzle</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 놀라거나 당황하여 정신을 차리지 못하게 얼떨떨한 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>Absentmindedly, not recovering composure, after a surprising or embarrassing situation.</dd><br>
<dt>멍하니 [멍ː하니]</dt><br>
<dd>blankly</dd><br>
<dd>정신이 나간 것처럼 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>(staying) Still as if one lost one's mind.</dd><br>
<dt>멍청히 [멍청히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. blankly</dd><br>
<dd>정신이 나간 것처럼 멍하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Absentmindedly as if one lost one's mind.</dd><br>
<dd>2. (no equivalent expression)</dd><br>
<dd>일을 제대로 판단하지 못할 정도로 어리석게.</dd><br>
<dd>Stupidly enough not to judge an incident properly.</dd><br>
<dt>멀뚱멀뚱 [멀뚱멀뚱]</dt><br>
<dd>1. (no equivalent expression)</dd><br>
<dd>눈을 초점 없이 뜨고 멍청하게 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one staring at space absentmindedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. blankly</dd><br>
<dd>눈만 둥그렇게 뜨고 생각 없이 물끄러미 쳐다보는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing someone opening their eyes wide and staring at someone or something without thinking.</dd><br>
<dt>멀거니 [멀거니]</dt><br>
<dd>vacantly; blankly</dd><br>
<dd>정신을 차리지 않은 채로 한 곳을 움직이지 않고 바라보고 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of looking at something in a daze, without movements.</dd><br>
<dt>망연히 [망연히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. remotely</dd><br>
<dd>매우 넓고 멀어서 아득하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Dimly because a place is very spacious and far away.</dd><br>
<dd>2. vacantly; blankly</dd><br>
<dd>정신이 나간 것처럼 멍하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Stupidly as if one lost one's mind.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>